@startuml sequence_admin_management
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Admin Inquiry Management (L2-019)

actor Admin
participant "InquiriesPage\n/admin/inquiries" as Page
participant "GET\n/api/inquiries" as ListAPI
participant "PUT\n/api/inquiries/[id]" as UpdateAPI
database "inquiries.inquiries" as DB

== Load & Filter ==
Admin -> Page: Navigate to /admin/inquiries
Page -> ListAPI: GET /api/inquiries
ListAPI -> DB: SELECT all inquiries
DB --> ListAPI: Inquiry[]
ListAPI --> Page: 200 { data, total }
Page --> Admin: Render data table

Admin -> Page: Filter by category="ambassador"
Page -> ListAPI: GET ?category=ambassador
ListAPI -> DB: SELECT WHERE\ncategory = "ambassador"
DB --> ListAPI: Filtered results
ListAPI --> Page: 200 { data, total }

== Review & Update ==
Admin -> Page: Click inquiry row
Page --> Admin: Detail modal/slide-over
Admin -> Page: Update status to "under-review"
Page -> UpdateAPI: PUT { status: "under-review" }
UpdateAPI -> DB: UPDATE status
DB --> UpdateAPI: Updated inquiry
UpdateAPI --> Page: 200 Inquiry
Page --> Admin: Status badge updated

== Export ==
Admin -> Page: Click "Export CSV"
Page -> Page: Generate CSV from\ncurrent filtered data
Page --> Admin: Download CSV file

@enduml
